reviewText: LOVE THE MAGICIAN ASPECT OF THIS.  IT'S CUTE.  AS ALWAYS, MY SERVICE WAS PERFECT AS WELL!

I bought this dvd for my daughter, not knowing that it is a mini-dvd.  The story is ok, but not worth $6.98. Amazon should have a separate category for the mini-dvd.  Nowhere in the description is it mentioned and I had no way of knowing until the product actually showed up
